// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1854 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a63a207f-9355-5211-8aac-58c4056116b5

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.04*")
